Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,So it's the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,启程前往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:35.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,前方将会是 Dawn dawn dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:09.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Take it
